<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قَالَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٧٦ - نا ابْنُ عُيَيْنَةَ , وَأَخْبَرَنِي مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ سُوقَةَ , عَنْ عِكْرِمَةَ ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«مَا كَانَ ثَمَنُهَا إِلَّا ثَلَاثَةَ دَنَانِيرَ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>